0.title: Session data volume (top 10)
0.query:
fetch logs
| filter index=="uberagent" and sourcetype=="uberAgent:CitrixSession:VirtualChannelDetail"
| parse content,"JSON:json"
| fieldsAdd  
VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputMB = json[VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputMB],
VirtualChannelDataVolumeOutputMB = json[VirtualChannelDataVolumeOutputMB],
SessionGUID = json[SessionGUID],
SessionUser = json[SessionUser]
| summarize {
    `Iutput volume (MB)`=sum(round(toDouble(VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputMB),decimals:1)),
    `Output volume (MB)`=sum(round(toDouble(VirtualChannelDataVolumeOutputMB),decimals:1)),
    `Input+Output (MB)`=sum(round(toDouble(VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputMB),decimals:1)+round(toDouble(VirtualChannelDataVolumeOutputMB),decimals:1)),
    User=takeLast(SessionUser),
    Host=takeLast(host)
},by:{SessionGUID}
| fieldsAdd UserHost = concat(User, "@", Host)
| sort `Input+Output (MB)` desc
| limit 10

1.title: Data table
1.query:
// Data table
fetch logs
|filter index=="uberagent" AND sourcetype=="uberAgent:Session:SessionDetail"
and sessionid!="0"
|parse content,"JSON:json"
|fieldsAdd SessionUser=json[SessionUser], 
SessionGUID=json[SessionGUID],
SessionConnectionState=json[SessionConnectionState],
SessionLogonTime=json[SessionLogonTime]
|summarize 
{
    UniqueSessions=countdistinct(sessionid),
    LastSeen=takeLast(timestamp),
    `Logon time`=max(SessionLogonTime),
    User=takeLast(SessionUser),
    Host=takeLast(host),
    SessionLast=takeLast(SessionConnectionState)
},by:{SessionGUID}
| fields SessionGUID,User,Host,
`Logon time`,
`Last seen`=LastSeen,
`Last state`=SessionLast
|join [
    //VirtualChannelDetail
    fetch logs
    | filter index=="uberagent" and sourcetype=="uberAgent:CitrixSession:VirtualChannelDetail"
    | parse content,"JSON:json"
    | fieldsAdd VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputOutputMB=toDouble(json[VirtualChannelDataVolumeOutputMB])+toDouble(json[VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputMB]),
    SessionGUID=json[SessionGUID]
    | summarize 
    {
        `Total data volume`=sum(VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputOutputMB),
        `Avg. data volume`=avg(VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputOutputMB)
    },by:{SessionGUID}
    | fields `Avg. data volume`,`Total data volume`, SessionGUID

], on:{SessionGUID}
| fieldsRename   `Avg. data volume`= `right.Avg. data volume`
| fieldsRename  `Total data volume`=`right.Total data volume`
| fieldsRemove SessionGUID,"right.*"

2.title: Session data volume over time
2.query:
fetch logs
| filter index=="uberagent" and sourcetype=="uberAgent:CitrixSession:VirtualChannelDetail"
| parse content,"JSON:json"
| fieldsAdd  
VirtualChannelDataVolumeOutputMB = json[VirtualChannelDataVolumeOutputMB],
VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputMB = json[VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputMB]
| makeTimeseries  {
    `Input volume`=avg(toDouble(VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputMB)),
    `Output volume`=sum(toDouble(VirtualChannelDataVolumeOutputMB))
}

4.content:
## Citrix Session Protocol Insights

5.title: Average ICA latency/ICA RTT over time
5.query:
fetch logs
| filter index=="uberagent" 
and sourcetype=="uberAgent:Session:SessionDetail"  and sessionid!="0"
| parse content,"JSON:json"
| fieldsAdd SessionRpLatencyMs=toDouble(json[SessionRpLatencyMs2]),
SessionRoundTripTimeMs=toDouble(json[SessionRoundTripTimeMs])
| makeTimeseries  
{
    `Avg. ICA latency (ms)`=avg(SessionRpLatencyMs),
    `Avg. ICA round-trip time (ms)`=avg(toDouble(SessionRoundTripTimeMs))
}

| summarize result=avg(SessionRoundTripTimeMs)

9.title: #Sessions:

| filter index=="uberagent" and sourcetype=="uberAgent:CitrixSession:VirtualChannelDetail"
| parse content,"JSON:json"
| fieldsAdd Sessions=json[SessionGUID]
| summarize NUM=countDistinct(Sessions)

14.title: Avg. session data volume/hour:
14.query:
fetch logs
| filter index=="uberagent" and sourcetype=="uberAgent:CitrixSession:VirtualChannelDetail"
| parse content,"JSON:json"
| fieldsAdd SumSessionDataVolumeMB=toDouble(json[VirtualChannelDataVolumeOutputMB])+toDouble(json[VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputMB])
| summarize SumSessionDataVolumeMB=sum(SumSessionDataVolumeMB)/toDouble($hours)

15.title: Average ICA latency/ICA round-trip time (top 10)
15.query:
fetch logs
| filter index=="uberagent" and sourcetype=="uberAgent:Session:SessionDetail"
| parse content,"JSON:json"
| fieldsAdd  
SessionRpLatencyMs = toDouble(json[SessionRpLatencyMs2]),
SessionRoundTripTimeMs = toDouble(json[SessionRoundTripTimeMs]),
SessionGUID = json[SessionGUID],
SessionUser = json[SessionUser]
| summarize {
    SessionRpLatencyMs=avg(toDouble(SessionRpLatencyMs)),
    SessionRoundTripTimeMs=avg(toDouble(SessionRoundTripTimeMs)),
    User=takeLast(SessionUser),
    Host=takeLast(host)
},by:{SessionGUID}
| filter isNotNull(SessionRpLatencyMs)
| sort SessionRpLatencyMs desc
| fieldsAdd UserHost = concat(User, "@", Host)
| limit 10

16.title: Virtual channel usage
16.query:
data record(name = "Virtual channel(s) in use", num= toLong($VcInUse)),
     record(name = "Virtual channel(s) not in use", num= toLong($VcNotInUse))

17.title: Virtual channel list
17.query:
// Virtual channel list
fetch logs
| filter index=="uberagent" and sourcetype=="uberAgent:CitrixSession:VirtualChannelDetail"
| parse content,"JSON:json"
| fieldsAdd 
VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputOutputMB=toDouble(json[VirtualChannelDataVolumeOutputMB])+toDouble(json[VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputMB]),
VirtualChannelVendorName=json[VirtualChannelVendorName]
| summarize SumSessionDataVolumeMB=round(sum(VirtualChannelDataVolumeInputOutputMB),decimals:1), 
by: {VirtualChannelVendorName}
| fieldsAdd VcInUse=if(SumSessionDataVolumeMB>0,1,else:0),
VcNotInUse=if(SumSessionDataVolumeMB<=0,1,else:0)
| fieldsRename `Total data volume (MB)`=SumSessionDataVolumeMB,
`Virtual channel` = VirtualChannelVendorName
| fields `Virtual channel`, `Total data volume (MB)`
| sort `Total data volume (MB)` Desc
